descript.abstract: Data set was initially created by Miller Management. It was maintained by the Story County Planning and Zoning office until May 2004 for the purposes of maintaining an E911 map. Since May 2004 it has been maintained by the Story County Auditor's Office.
descript.purpose: The purpose of this data is to maintain an accurate centerline file for various purposes (i.e. general county map, geocoding, emergency response). This centerline file is updated on an "as needed" basis.

theme.themekt: Common reference name for roads coverages used for emergency purposes

idinfo.accconst: The only person who should maintain this file is the person serving in the Mapping Technician Position within the Auditor's office
idinfo.useconst: This coverage is not intended to be an exact account of the actual physical location of the roads represented. It is only to be used as an indication of the general location of the roads.
